                        "content": "After opening a paper, check whether structured blocks are already available. If not, run MinerU Parse. Once blocks are available, switch to linked reading mode. Click a block on the right side and observe how the PDF moves to the corresponding location. Then click a PDF region and observe how the block view reacts. This interaction is the foundation of PaperQuay’s reading model. "
